# Branch 3.x (upcoming stable)

This is the main branch of **awesome** and gets all new features and bug fixes.

Latest upcoming stable version of **awesome** is version 3.0-rc2 (codename: *Wake Up Call*) released on 8th August 2008.

* [awesome-3.0-rc2.tar.gz](awesome-3.0-rc2.tar.gz)
* [awesome-3.0-rc2.tar.bz2](awesome-3.0-rc2.tar.bz2)

# Branch 2.x (old stable)

This branch of **awesome** is still maintained but get only bug fixes.

Latest old stable version of **awesome** is version 2.3.3 (codename: *Pure Morning*) released on 26th July 2008.

* [v2.3.3 changelog](/changelogs/v2.3.3) ([short](/changelogs/short/v2.3.3))
* [awesome-2.3.3.tar.gz](awesome-2.3.3.tar.gz)
* [awesome-2.3.3.tar.bz2](awesome-2.3.3.tar.bz2)

# Developement

Developement versions of **awesome** can be downloaded as tarballs using git snapshot [here](http://git.naquadah.org/?p=awesome.git;a=summary).

You can also grab a git copy by running:

  `git clone git://git.naquadah.org/awesome.git`

